        "content": "Xagons: Building Blocks for Activity-Based Design.  Design is about more than physical artifacts, it is about human activities. Design is also too important to do with only one side of your brain. To promote a holistic design approach that uses whole-brain thinking to reshape human activities for the better, we have created XAGONs. These are physical cards whose two sides support and connect the two complementary modes of design thinking: rational, left-brained analysis and intuitive, right-brained ideation. Authors: Darren Edge, Sergio Paolanton",
